div.span: Print 'The number must be greater than 6.'
Create a list SieveList of N bools, all entries false
While there are entries true in the SieveList
Determine k such that k-th entry of SieveList is the first with entry true
Set k-th entry of SieveList to false
Set m*k^2-th entry of SieveList to false for all multiples m*k^2 of k^2
